// Saturn Valley Coffee Sequence
l_0xe10000:
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]You've traveled very far from"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]home..."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Do you remember how your long"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]and winding journey began with"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]someone pounding at your door?"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]It was Porky, the worst person in"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]your neighborhood, who knocked"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]on the door that fateful night."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]On your way, you have walked,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]thought and fought.  Yet through"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]all this, you have never lost your"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]courage. You have grown steadily"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]stronger, though you have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]experienced the pain of battle"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]many times."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]You are no longer alone in your"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]adventure, [ 08 02 ] who is"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]steadfast, kind and even pretty,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]is always at your side."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ][ 08 03 ] is with you as well."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Though he is timid, he came from"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]a distant land to help you."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ][ 08 01 ], as you certainly"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]know by now, you are not a"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]regular young man...  You have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]an awesome destiny to fulfill."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]The journey from this point will"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]be long, and it will be more"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]difficult than anything you have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]undergone to this point.  Yet, I"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]know you will be all right.  When"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]good battles evil, which side do"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]you believe wins?  Do you have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]faith that good is triumphant?"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]One thing you must never lose is"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]courage.  If you believe in the"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]goal you are striving for, you will"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]be courageous.  There are many"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]difficult times ahead, but you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]must keep your sense of humor,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]work through the tough"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]situations and enjoy yourself."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]When you have finished this cup"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]of coffee, your adventure will"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]begin again.  Next, you must pass"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]through a vast desert and"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]proceed to the big city of"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Fourside."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ][ 08 01 ]..."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]           [ 08 02 ]..."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]                      [ 08 03 ]..."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]             May the goddess"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]              of good fortune"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]         smile upon you always..."
