// Tenda Village Tea Sequence
l_0xe10652:
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Like a great tapestry, vertical and"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]horizontal threads have met and"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]become intertwined, creating a"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]huge, beautiful image."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]You may have cursed this never-"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]ending journey.  You have known"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]injury and defeat, but you have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]struggled on to reach this place."
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Your in-born wisdom and"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]courage have helped bring you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]here.  You have believed in your"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]friends, and as a group, you have"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]supported each other.  Have you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]ever stopped to consider how"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]much your power has grown?"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Now, you could fell enemies in"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Onett and Twoson with one"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]blow.  As you certainly know,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]you cannot turn back.  Giygas,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]the arch fiend of the universe, is"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]growing frightened of you and"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]your power.  He is searching for"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]ways to end your journey."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]From here, the challenge grows"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]and your adventure will take you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]beyond anything you ever"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]imagined.  You are drawing near"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]to Giygas.  Remember, when you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]are suffering hardships, your"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]enemy is also struggling."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]Still, where DID Porky go,"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]anyway?  When this cup of"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]tea is finished, your adventure will"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]continue.  Your destiny pulls you"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]in the right direction.  Believe in"
	"[ 09 ][ 01 0C ]yourself and press forward."
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
	"[ 09 ]"
